{"id":122397,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：诈骗犯马多夫家当高价拍卖/","date":"2010-11-15T08:07:16Z","modified":"2010-11-15T08:07:16Z","title":"简讯：诈骗犯马多夫家当高价拍卖","content":"<div>\n<p>华尔街世纪巨骗马多夫的豪华手表、钢琴以及其他不义之财周六（13日）在纽约拍卖会上高价卖出。</p>\n<p>这次拍卖一共卖了两百万美元，将赔偿马多夫金融骗局的受害者。</p>\n<p>拍卖的物品包括马多夫的首饰，金表和艺术品以及他穿用过的袜子和内衣。</p>\n<p>马多夫因骗取投资人好几百亿美金判刑150年，目前正在服刑。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-vcoBSsun0FjXusF-6NZk6XNCpY/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-vcoBSsun0FjXusF-6NZk6XNCpY/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-vcoBSsun0FjXusF-6NZk6XNCpY/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-vcoBSsun0FjXusF-6NZk6XNCpY/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=QFRQ_RNVE88:t1L_CxTrUnI:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=QFRQ_RNVE88:t1L_CxTrUnI:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=QFRQ_RNVE88:t1L_CxTrUnI:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=QFRQ_RNVE88:t1L_CxTrUnI:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=QFRQ_RNVE88:t1L_CxTrUnI:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=QFRQ_RNVE88:t1L_CxTrUnI:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/QFRQ_RNVE88\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk